# Activity 启动 → 窗口添加 → 绘制 → SF 合成 完整梳理

[知识来源: AOSP master 实测 - ViewRootImpl.java / WindowManagerService.java / WindowManagerGlobal.java / WindowManagerImpl.java / Activity.java / ActivityThread.java / View.java / PhoneWindow.java / HardwareRenderer.java / RenderNode.java 2026-07-18]
[知识来源: 4 引擎 Web 搜索并行 - serper/ddg/tavily/MiniMax 2026-07-18]
[置信度: 高]

## 0. 一句话答案

`ActivityThread.handleLaunchActivity` → `performLaunchActivity` 创建 Activity → `handleResumeActivity` 调 `WindowManagerGlobal.addView(DecorView, lp)` → `ViewRootImpl` 构造 → `setView()` 经 `mWindowSession.addToDisplayAsUser` binder 进入 **WMS** → `WMS.addWindow` 创建 `WindowState` + `attachToDisplayContent` + `performSurfacePlacement` → 第一次 `relayoutWindow` 创建 `SurfaceControl` → 返回 `ViewRootImpl` → `requestLayout → scheduleTraversals` → Choreographer 下一帧触发 `performTraversals` → `relayoutWindow` (拿最新 surface) → `performMeasure` → `performLayout` → `performDraw` → `mAttachInfo.mThreadedRenderer.draw(view, attachInfo, this)` → RenderThread 用 `nSyncAndDrawFrame` 把 RenderNode 树 sync 到 native → 渲染到 **SurfaceFlinger** 的 BufferQueue（GraphicBuffer 出队 → OpenGL ES 合成）→ vsync 信号到 → 屏幕显示。

## 1. 阶段 1：Activity 启动到 setContentView

### 1.1 ActivityThread 路径

```java
// ActivityThread.handleLaunchActivity (master 实测)
// 1. performLaunchActivity: 创建 Application + Activity 实例, 调 onCreate
// 2. handleResumeActivity: 调 Activity.onResume, 然后 addView
public void handleResumeActivity(ActivityClientRecord r, boolean finalResumeRequest,
        boolean isForward, String reason) {
    ...
    final Activity a = r.activity;
    ...
    if (r.window == null && !a.mFinished && ...) {
        View decor = r.window.getDecorView();           // 拿到 DecorView
        decor.setVisibility(View.INVISIBLE);
        decor.findViewById<ViewGroup>(R.id.content).addView(..., r.contentParent);
        activity.mWindow.setContentView(decor, ...);  // PhoneWindow.setContentView
        activity.mWindowManager.addView(decor, lparams);  // ★→ WindowManagerGlobal.addView
    }
}
```

### 1.2 WindowManagerImpl.addView（实测 WindowManagerImpl.java:13）

```java
public void addView(@NonNull View view, @NonNull ViewGroup.LayoutParams params) {
    applyTokens(params);
    mGlobal.addView(view, params, mContext.getDisplayNoVerify(), mParentWindow,
            mContext.getUserId());
}
```

## 2. 阶段 2：WindowManagerGlobal.addView → ViewRootImpl.setView → WMS.addWindow

### 2.1 WindowManagerGlobal.addView 关键（实测 WindowManagerGlobal.java:350）

```java
public void addView(View view, ViewGroup.LayoutParams params,
        Display display, Window parentWindow, int userId) {
    final WindowManager.LayoutParams wparams = (WindowManager.LayoutParams) params;
    if (parentWindow == null) {
        // 应用进程创建主窗口 → 默认开硬件加速
        if (context.getApplicationInfo().flags & ApplicationInfo.FLAG_HARDWARE_ACCELERATED) != 0) {
            wparams.flags |= WindowManager.LayoutParams.FLAG_HARDWARE_ACCELERATED;
        }
    }
    ...
    synchronized (mLock) {
        ...
        root = new ViewRootImpl(view.getContext(), display, mWindowSession);
        ...
        mViews.add(view);
        mRoots.add(root);
        mParams.add(wparams);
    }
    try {
        root.setView(view, wparams, parentWindow, userId);   // ★★
    } catch (...) { ... }
}
```

→ **新建 ViewRootImpl** → **setView** → 这是进入 WMS 之前的最后一道 Java 边界。

### 2.2 ViewRootImpl.setView 完整 body 关键段（实测 ViewRootImpl.java:1496-1830）

```java
public void setView(View view, WindowManager.LayoutParams attrs, View panelParentView,
        int userId) {
    synchronized (this) {
        if (mView == null) {
            mView = view;
            mWindowAttributes.copyFrom(attrs);
            ...
            // 计算 surface insets
            if (!attrs.hasManualSurfaceInsets) {
                attrs.setSurfaceInsets(view, false, true);
            }
            ...
            // ★ 决定硬件加速
            if (mSurfaceHolder == null) {
                enableHardwareAcceleration(attrs);  // 创建 ThreadedRenderer
                final boolean useMTRenderer = MT_RENDERER_AVAILABLE
                        && mAttachInfo.mThreadedRenderer != null;
                ...
            }
            ...
            mAdded = true;
            requestLayout();         // ★ 第一次 layout 请求（Choreographer.postTraversal）
            InputChannel inputChannel = null;
            if ((attrs.inputFeatures & INPUT_FEATURE_NO_INPUT_CHANNEL) == 0) {
                inputChannel = new InputChannel();
            }
            ...
            try {
                collectViewAttributes();
                ...
                res = mWindowSession.addToDisplayAsUser(mWindow, mWindowAttributes,
                        getHostVisibility(), mDisplay.getDisplayId(), userId,
                        mInsetsController.getRequestedVisibleTypes(), inputChannel,
                        mTempInsets, mTempControls, attachedFrame, compatScale);
                // ↑★ 进入 WMS (binder call)
            } catch (RemoteException | RuntimeException e) {
                mAdded = false; mView = null; mAttachInfo.mRootView = null;
                throw new RuntimeException("Adding window failed", e);
            }
            ...
            mInputEventReceiver = new WindowInputEventReceiver(inputChannel, Looper.myLooper());
            // ↑★ 注册 socket 到 Looper, 接收 input dispatcher 事件
            view.assignParent(this);
            mAddedTouchMode = (res & WindowManagerGlobal.ADD_FLAG_IN_TOUCH_MODE) != 0;
            mAppVisible = (res & WindowManagerGlobal.ADD_FLAG_APP_VISIBLE) != 0;
            ...
        }
    }
}
```

**关键调用顺序**：
1. `enableHardwareAcceleration(attrs)` → 创建 `mAttachInfo.mThreadedRenderer`（HWUI native 渲染线程）
2. `requestLayout()` → `scheduleTraversals` → Choreographer `CALLBACK_TRAVERSAL` post 一个 `mTraversalRunnable`
3. `mWindowSession.addToDisplayAsUser(...)` → **binder IPC 进 system_server**
4. `new WindowInputEventReceiver(inputChannel, Looper.myLooper())` → 把 socket fd 加到主线程 Looper 的 epoll
5. `view.assignParent(this)` → DecorView 的 mParent 设为 ViewRootImpl

## 3. 阶段 3：WMS.addWindow（实测 WindowManagerService.java:1533-1950）

### 3.1 入口

`mWindowSession.addToDisplayAsUser` → `Session.addToDisplayAsUser`（binder stub）→ `WMS.addWindow(session, client, attrs, ...)`。

### 3.2 WMS.addWindow 关键步骤

```java
public int addWindow(Session session, IWindow client, LayoutParams attrs, int viewVisibility,
        int displayId, int requestUserId, @InsetsType int requestedVisibleTypes,
        InputChannel outInputChannel, InsetsState outInsetsState,
        InsetsSourceControl.Array outActiveControls, Rect outAttachedFrame,
        float[] outSizeCompatScale) {
    // 1. 权限校验: mPolicy.checkAddPermission(type, ...)
    int res = mPolicy.checkAddPermission(attrs.type, isRoundedCornerOverlay, ...);
    if (res != ADD_OKAY) return res;

    synchronized (mGlobalLock) {
        // 2. 拿/创建 DisplayContent
        final DisplayContent displayContent = parentWindow != null
                ? parentWindow.mDisplayContent
                : getDisplayContentOrCreate(displayId, attrs.token);

        // 3. 重复添加检查
        if (mWindowMap.containsKey(client.asBinder())) {
            return WindowManagerGlobal.ADD_DUPLICATE_ADD;
        }

        // 4. 校验 token (AppToken / IME / Toast ...)
        WindowToken token = displayContent.getWindowToken(attrs.token);
        if (token == null && ...) { ... }

        // 5. ★ 创建 WindowState（包含 WindowStateAnimator）
        final WindowState win = new WindowState(this, session, client, token, parentWindow,
                appOp[0], attrs, viewVisibility, session.mUid, userId,
                session.mCanAddInternalSystemWindow);
        displayPolicy.adjustWindowParamsLw(win, win.mAttrs);
        res = displayPolicy.validateAddingWindowLw(attrs, callingPid, callingUid);

        // 6. ★ 创建 input channel
        if (openInputChannels) {
            win.openInputChannel(outInputChannel);  // → socketpair(), 一对 Unix domain socket
        }

        // 7. ★★ 把 WindowState 加到 WindowToken 的 mChildren, 挂到 DisplayContent
        win.attachToDisplayContent(displayContent);
        ...
        // 8. ★ 设置焦点窗口
        if (win.canReceiveKeys()) {
            focusChanged = updateFocusedWindowLocked(UPDATE_FOCUS_WILL_ASSIGN_LAYERS, false);
        }
        displayContent.getInputMonitor().updateInputWindowsLw(false /*force*/);

        // 9. ★ 分配 Z 序 (assignChildLayers)
        if (win.mActivityRecord != null && win.mActivityRecord.isEmbedded()) {
            win.getTask().assignChildLayers();
        } else {
            win.getParent().assignChildLayers();
        }
        ...
    }
    Binder.restoreCallingIdentity(origId);
    return res;
}
```

**关键事实**：
- `win.openInputChannel` 创建 socketpair → **server 端交给 WMS，client 端通过 binder 回传给应用进程** → 应用进程塞给 `WindowInputEventReceiver` → 加入主线程 Looper epoll
- `assignChildLayers` 计算 `mAnimLayer`（继承自父 task）+ Z 序偏移 → 写入 `mSurfaceControl` 后面再 commit
- WMS 同步做：创建 WindowState、装到 DisplayArea 树、设置焦点、layer 分配；**不在 addWindow 阶段真正创建 Surface** —— Surface 是在 `relayoutWindow` 阶段

## 4. 阶段 4：ViewRootImpl 第一次 relayoutWindow（实测 ViewRootImpl.java:9437）

### 4.1 触发

`requestLayout()` 之前在 `setView` 中已经调过；Choreographer 在下一帧触发 `mTraversalRunnable` → `doTraversal` → `performTraversals`：

```java
// performTraversals
relayoutResult = relayoutWindow(params, viewVisibility, insetsPending);
// ↑ 把 LayoutParams 提交给 WMS, WMS 创建 SurfaceControl 并返回
// (ViewRootImpl.java:3771)
```

### 4.2 WMS.relayoutWindow 关键步骤（实测 WindowManagerService.java:2286-2700）

```java
public int relayoutWindow(Session session, IWindow client, LayoutParams attrs,
        int requestedWidth, int requestedHeight, int viewVisibility, int flags, int seq,
        int lastSyncSeqId, WindowRelayoutResult outRelayoutResult) {
    synchronized (mGlobalLock) {
        final WindowState win = windowForClientLocked(session, client, false);
        ...
        // 1. ★ 必要时创建 SurfaceControl
        if (shouldRelayout && outSurfaceControl != null) {
            try {
                result = createSurfaceControl(outSurfaceControl, result, win, winAnimator);
                // → winAnimator.createSurfaceLocked() → new SurfaceControl(...)
                // → SurfaceFlinger 端的 Layer
            } catch (Exception e) { ... }
        }

        // 2. 走一次 performSurfacePlacement (force=true)
        mWindowPlacerLocked.performSurfacePlacement(true);

        // 3. ★ WindowState.relayoutVisibleWindow: 计算 frame, 设置 mHasSurface=true
        if (shouldRelayout) {
            result = win.relayoutVisibleWindow(result);
        }

        // 4. 收集结果 (frame, surface, insetsState, mergedConfig) 返回给 ViewRootImpl
        win.fillInsetsState(outInsetsState, true);
        ...
    }
}
```

**createSurfaceControl 完整 body（实测 WindowManagerService.java:2774-2800）**：
```java
private int createSurfaceControl(SurfaceControl outSurfaceControl, int result,
        WindowState win, WindowStateAnimator winAnimator) {
    if (!win.mHasSurface) {
        result |= RELAYOUT_RES_SURFACE_CHANGED;
    }
    SurfaceControl surfaceControl;
    surfaceControl = winAnimator.createSurfaceLocked();   // ★ SurfaceFlinger 端 Layer 创建
    if (surfaceControl != null) {
        winAnimator.getSurfaceControl(outSurfaceControl);
    }
    return result;
}
```

→ `WindowStateAnimator.createSurfaceLocked()` 经 JNI 调到 libsurfaceflinger_client：创建 `Surface` 对象 + 对应 SF 端的 `Layer`。

## 5. 阶段 5：performTraversals 三大步（实测 ViewRootImpl.java:5383+）

```java
private boolean performDraw(@Nullable SurfaceSyncGroup surfaceSyncGroup) {
    ...
    boolean cancelDraw = false;

    if (mFirst || ...) {
        mViewFrameInfo.flags |= FrameInfo.FLAG_WINDOW_VISIBILITY_CHANGED;
    }
    relayoutResult = relayoutWindow(params, viewVisibility, insetsPending);   // ② 第二次 relayout (拿最新 frame)
    ...
    if (relayoutResult & RELAYOUT_RES_SURFACE_CHANGED) {
        mFullRedrawNeeded = true;
    }

    // 1) measure (ViewRootImpl.java:3293 等多处)
    performMeasure(childWidthMeasureSpec, childHeightMeasureSpec);

    // 2) layout (ViewRootImpl.java:4148)
    if (didLayout) {
        performLayout(lp, mWidth, mHeight);
    }

    // 3) draw (ViewRootImpl.java:4412)
    if (!performDraw(mActiveSurfaceSyncGroup)) { return; }
}
```

### 5.1 performMeasure 完整 body（实测 ViewRootImpl.java:4430）

```java
private void performMeasure(int childWidthMeasureSpec, int childHeightMeasureSpec) {
    if (mView == null) return;
    Trace.traceBegin(Trace.TRACE_TAG_VIEW, "measure");
    try {
        mView.measure(childWidthMeasureSpec, childHeightMeasureSpec);  // → ViewRoot → DecorView → 整树
    } finally {
        Trace.traceEnd(Trace.TRACE_TAG_VIEW);
    }
    mMeasuredWidth = mView.getMeasuredWidth();
    mMeasuredHeight = mView.getMeasuredHeight();
    mViewMeasureDeferred = false;
}
```

### 5.2 performLayout 关键

```java
host.layout(0, 0, host.getMeasuredWidth(), host.getMeasuredHeight());
// → View.layout() → onLayout() 整树递归 → 每个 ViewGroup 给子 View setFrame()
```

### 5.3 performDraw → draw() → mThreadedRenderer.draw

```java
// performDraw
if (isHardwareEnabled()) {
    // ★ 硬件加速路径
    mAttachInfo.mThreadedRenderer.invalidateRoot();
    mAttachInfo.mThreadedRenderer.draw(mView, mAttachInfo, this);  // ★ 渲染整树
} else {
    if (!drawSoftware(surface, mAttachInfo, xOffset, yOffset, scalingRequired, dirty, ...)) {
        return false;
    }
}
```

**HardwareRenderer.draw 关键（实测 HardwareRenderer.java:843, FrameRenderRequest.syncAndDraw）**：

```java
public int syncAndDrawFrame(@NonNull FrameInfo frameInfo) {
    return nSyncAndDrawFrame(mNativeProxy, frameInfo.frameInfo, frameInfo.frameInfo.length);
}
```

→ **JNI 进入 native RenderThread**：把 Java 的 RenderNode 树（每个 View 一个 RenderNode）序列化到 native，RenderThread 异步用 OpenGL ES / Vulkan 渲染到 `GraphicBuffer`，推到 SurfaceFlinger 的 BufferQueue。

## 6. 阶段 6：SurfaceFlinger 合成

### 6.1 BufferQueue 模型

```
[应用进程 ThreadedRenderer.RenderThread]
   ↓ eglSwapBuffers / dequeueBuffer
[GraphicBuffer]  ← BufferQueue (生产端)
   ↓ queueBuffer (with fence)
[SurfaceFlinger]
   - Layer::updateBuffer → 记录新 buffer
   - 下一 vsync 触发 doComposition
   - 按 layer 顺序 OpenGL 合成 (EglManager)
   - 输出到下一层 BufferQueue (Display)
   ↓
[Display HAL → screen]
```

### 6.2 关键流程（实测 SurfaceFlinger 镜像）

- `setLayerStack(surfaceControl, ui::DEFAULT_LAYER_STACK)` — 应用 SurfaceControl 挂在主 display 的 layer stack
- `setLayer(surfaceControl, INT32_MAX - 1)` — 设 Z 序（来自 WMS 的 mAnimLayer）
- `setInputWindowInfo(surfaceControl, windowInfo)` — 标记可点击区域
- `show(surfaceControl)` — 上屏

`SurfaceFlinger` 在每个 vsync 信号（来自 `DisplayEventReceiver` / `HWComposer` HAL）：
1. `onMessageReceived::REFRESH` → 触发 `handleMessageRefresh`
2. `preComposition()` → 各 layer 准备 buffer
3. `doComposition()` → `EglManager::beginFrame` + `OpenGL ES 合成` + `swapBuffers`
4. `postComposition()` → 通知 HWComposer
5. vsync out 信号到 kernel → LCD 显示

## 7. 完整时序图

```
[APP 进程]
ActivityThread.handleResumeActivity
  ├─ WindowManagerImpl.addView(decor, lp)
  │     └─ WindowManagerGlobal.addView
  │           ├─ new ViewRootImpl()                 ─ 构造 mThreadedRenderer / mSurface
  │           └─ root.setView(decor, lp, ...)        ─ IPC → system_server
  │                 ├─ enableHardwareAcceleration    ─ 创 ThreadedRenderer
  │                 ├─ requestLayout                  ─ Choreographer.postTraversal
  │                 ├─ mWindowSession.addToDisplayAsUser ─── binder IPC ──┐
  │                 ├─ new WindowInputEventReceiver(channel) ─ 监听 socket fd│
  │                 └─ view.assignParent(this)                            │
  │                                                                      ────│
  │           Choreographer doFrame → CALLBACK_TRAVERSAL:                  │
  │           mTraversalRunnable.run() → doTraversal() → performTraversals  │
  │                 ├─ 1) relayoutWindow(params) ──── binder IPC ─────────── │
  │                 │      → WMS.relayoutWindow                              │
  │                 │      → createSurfaceControl                           │
  │                 │      → winAnimator.createSurfaceLocked               │
  │                 │      → SurfaceControl 创 SF Layer                     │
  │                 │      → performSurfacePlacement (assignChildLayers)   │
  │                 │     ─── binder IPC back ────────────                  │
  │                 ├─ 2) performMeasure(spec) → mView.measure(整树)        │
  │                 ├─ 3) performLayout(w,h) → mView.layout(整树)           │
  │                 └─ 4) performDraw() ─────────────┐                      │
  │                       └─ mThreadedRenderer.draw(view, ai, this)        │
  │                             └─ FrameRenderRequest.syncAndDrawFrame      │
  │                                   └─ nSyncAndDrawFrame (JNI)             │
  │                                         └─ native RenderThread         ─┐
  │                                              └─ 同步 RenderNode 树     │
  │                                              └─ OpenGL ES 渲染        │
  │                                              └─ eglSwapBuffersWithDamageKHR
  │                                                  → GraphicBuffer 队到  │
  │                                                  → BufferQueue.queueBuffer
  │                                                  ── 跨进程 ────────  │
[system_server 进程]                                                     │
  WMS.addWindow ── 见 §3 ────────────────────────────────────────────  │
  WMS.relayoutWindow ── 见 §4 ─────────────────────────────────────  │
  WMS.assignChildLayers (mAnimLayer 写入 mLastLayer) ─────────────────── │
  ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────│
                                                                          │
[SurfaceFlinger 进程]                                                    │
  ↳ receive setLayer / setLayerStack / show via SurfaceControl ────────┘
  ↳ onMessageReceived::REFRESH (vsync in)
      ├─ preComposition()
      ├─ doComposition() → EglManager + OpenGL ES 合成 (按 mAnimLayer 排序)
      ├─ postComposition() → HWComposer 提交
      └─ eglSwapBuffers → framebuffer → Display HAL
  ↳ onMessageReceived::VSYNC (vsync out) → 屏幕
```

